Package: epilab
Type: Package
Title: EpiLab Functions for workflow implementation
Version: 0.5.2
Date: 2016-03-15
Authors@R: c(
  person('Gustavo', 'Fernandez Bayon', role=c('aut', 'cre'), email='fernandezgustavo@uniovi.es'),
  person('Isabel', 'Cobo Sanchez', role = c('aut'), email = 'icobo@carrerasresearch.org')
  )
Author: Gustavo Fernandez Bayon, Isabel Cobo Sanchez
Maintainer: Gustavo Fernandez Bayon <fernandezgustavo@uniovi.es>,
    Isabel Cobo Sanchez <icobo@carrerasresearch.org>
Description: Compilation of data, functions and other stuff intended to be used
    inside the EpiLab for the implementation of data processing workflows. Most
    of the functions are related to the analysis of Illumina 450k microarrays. In
    the future, this package might be splitted to take into account the different
    aspects of the lab workflows.
Depends:
    FDb.InfiniumMethylation.hg19,
    ggplot2,
    methods
